						<div class="comment-body"><p>It&#8217;s an interesting topic but I&#8217;m quite back on my readings on modern Europe. If there&#8217;s any good and accessible source out there I&#8217;d like to take a look some time. </p>
<p>Of course the dynamics of Europe and China are very different; the sheer competition.</p>
</div>

			<div class="reply">
				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2014/02/08/monarchy-and-monarchs/?replytocom=4330#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-4330", "4330", "respond", "1578")'>Reply</a>			</div>
